WEBVTT

00:02.039 --> 00:03.407
A dragon is coming.

00:04.543 --> 00:05.981
Come on, you beast!

00:08.679 --> 00:10.402
Stay together and we live.

00:11.414 --> 00:15.265
No, a slightly smaller dragon, tiny, really.

00:16.644 --> 00:18.761
But faster, way faster,...

00:20.321 --> 00:22.743
...and cuter, but not that cute.

